tspan.tspan: There are two ways two work with this template:
1. Reveal one of the provided grids, and with the snap tool
activated, fill it with your pixel art using the rectangle tool. Make sure
you're working in the "texture" clipped group. Repeat for the back
2. Import a bitmap or some other art and place it in the "texture"
